  <section class="section"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>Related KitchenAid and Whirlpool-family pages</h2>
    <ul class="related-links">
      <li><a href="/brands/kitchenaid/">KitchenAid brand hub (all categories) →</a></li>
